subject: United States Open Cup (Soccer)
Soccer
lead_paragraph: Sainey Touray had two goals, and Lucky Mkosana added another as the host Harrisburg City Islanders of the U.S.L. Pro Division upset the Red Bulls, 3-1, on Tuesday night in the fourth round of the Lamar Hunt U.S. Open Cup.
